RULES of variables declaration
===============================
1) must not start with number
2) must not use keywords, reserved words
3) SPACE between the names of variables is NOT allowed
4) special char like _ is allowed
   a$b=100  illegal as $ is not allowed
   a%b=100  illegal as % is not allowed
5) length of variable (technically can be v long) but the objective is meaningful
6) variable name are case sensitive 
   AGE = 10
   age = 20
   Age = 30
   AGe = 40
   agE = 50
   (all FIVE variables are DIFFERENT)

